snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 42 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 42 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 4th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar

Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.description:
ചിന്നക്കനാലിൽ നിന്ന് കാടുകടത്തിയ അരിക്കൊമ്പൻ ഇപ്പോൾ തമ്പടിച്ചിരിക്കുന്നത് തമിഴ്നാട് അതിർത്തി പ്രദേശമായ മേഘമലയിലാണ്. കഴിഞ്ഞ ദിവസം പുലർച്ചെ ഇവിടത്തെ ഇരവുങ്കല്ലാർ എസ്റ്റേറ്റിലെ ഒരു വീട് തള്ളിത്തുറന്ന് അരി എടുക്കുകയും ചെയ്തു. തുമ്പിക്കൈ വീടിനകത്തിട്ട് അരിച്ചാക്ക് തപ്പിയെടുത്ത് കൊണ്ടുപോവുകയായിരുന്നെന്ന് സംഭവത്തിന് ദൃക്സാക്ഷിയായ വീട്ടുടമസ്ഥൻ കറുപ്പസാമി പറയുന്നു.

snippet.title: Lifemates - a story of Husband & Wife | Episode 4 - Control or Care? | Web Series | Take A Break
snippet.description:

Rajauri Encounter: सरहद पर देश की सुरक्षा यूहीं नहीं हो जाती…इसके लिए जान की बाज़ी लगानी पड़ती है. हमारे देश के कितने ही बहादुर जवान हर पल हमें और आप लोगों को महफूज़ रखने के लिए Border पर सीना तान कर मुस्तैद खड़े हैं. इस मुस्तैदी की कीमत कभी देश के लिए जान देकर भी चुकानी पड़ती है. Jammu Kashmir के Rajauri में शुक्रवार को ऐसा ही हुआ. जहां देश ने अपने पांच वीर सैनिकों को हमेशा के लिए खो दिया. इन्हीं में से एक थे West Bengal के Siddhant Chhetri..Indian Army में कार्यरत दार्जिलिंग के रहने वाले राइफलमैन सिद्धांत छेत्री…जो कि 9 पैरा कमांडो थे…उनकी बलिदान देने की खबर से पूरे दार्जिलिंग में शोक की लहर दौड़ गई. पूरा परिवार शोक में डूब चुका है.

snippet.title: Manipur Violence News Updates: Shoot At Sight Orders In Extreme Conditions In Manipur | News18
snippet.description:
Manipur Violence News Updates: Shoot At Sight Orders In Extreme Conditions In Manipur | News18

Manipur Curfew Live Updates: The Indian Army on Friday said that the situation in Moreh and Kangpokpi areas was brought under control and is stable. It added that all efforts are underway to restore normalcy in Imphal and Churachandpur area. On Thursday, to contain spiraling violence in Manipur between tribals and the majority Meitei community which has displaced over 9,000 people from their villages, state government issued shoot at sight order in 'extreme cases'. Fifty-five columns of the Army and Assam Rifles had to be deployed to contain widespread rioting. Meanwhile, internet services remain suspended in Manipur for five day.

#manipurviolence #manipur #manipurnews #englishnews

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3764 - 6 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3764: Jasoos Bhide
--------------------------------------------------------
Bhide begins to have concerns about Tapu's motivations and makes the decision to keep an eye on him. Bhide gets into an auto and instructs the driver to keep driving in the same direction as Tapu and Sonu's vehicle. Bhide tries to bribe the vehicle driver after he refuses to obey his commands. When Tapu and Sonu are finally spotted entering a shrine, Bhide follows them as well. Bhide runs across one of his student's parents at the temple's stairs and strikes up a conversation with him. Bhide becomes impatient because it has caused a significant diversion from his stalking. See how Bhide flees when he is going to be caught by Tapu and Sonu in the act by watching the episode!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3764, 6 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Chandra Grahan 2023: आज लगेगा साल का पहला चंद्र ग्रहण, क्या इस देश में लगेगा भूकंप का ग्रहण?
snippet.description:
5 मई 2023 को साल का पहला चंद्र ग्रहण लगने जा रहा है. ज्योतिष शास्त्र के मुताबिक 139 साल बाद  बुद्ध पूर्णिमा पर चंद्रग्रहण लगने जा रहा है. इससे 15 दिन पहले साल का पहला सूर्यग्रहण 20 अप्रैल 2023 के दिन लगा था. साल का ये पहला चंद्र ग्रहण शुक्रवार 5 मई की रात 8 बजकर 44 मिनट से शुरू होगा और देर रात 1 बजकर 02 मिनट तक रहेगा. यानी कुल 4 घंटे 15 मिनट तक रहेगा. बड़ा सवाल ये है कि क्या चंद्र ग्रहण आने के बाद एक बार फिर किसी देश पर भूकंप का ग्रहण लग सकता है. क्या एक बार फिर किसी देश पर भूकंप की आपदा आ सकती है

snippet.title: Satyapal Malik Interview: पुलवामा, अरविंद केजरीवाल और बीजेपी पर क्या बोले सत्यपाल मलिक (BBC Hindi)
snippet.description:
जम्मू-कश्मीर के पूर्व राज्यपाल सत्यपाल मलिक ने बीबीसी हिन्दी से ख़ास बातचीत में कई मुद्दों पर अपनी राय रखी है. इस बातचीत में उन्होंने बीजेपी के साथ तय किए गए अपने सियासी सफ़र के बारे में बताया. साथ ही उन्होंने पुलवामा हमले पर दिए गए अपने बयान, केंद्र और दिल्ली सरकार के बीच चल रही उठापठक और देश के राजनीतिक भविष्य पर खुलकर अपनी बात रखी है.

इंटरव्यू: सर्वप्रिया सांगवान
शूट-एडिट:  शाहनवाज़ अहमद और शाद मिद्हत

#satypalmalik #pmmodi #pulwamaattack 

* जिन खबरों, तस्वीरों और दावों पर आपको हो शक, हम आपके लिए करेंगे उनकी परख. बीबीसी फ़ैक्ट चेक है आपके साथ. बस भेजिए WhatsApp मैसेज 9811520111 पर. बीबीसी फ़ैक्ट चेक यानी सच की कसौटी.

* Corona Virus से जुड़े और दिलचस्प वीडियो देखने के लिए यहां क्लिक करें : https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=npgvIvfmNkE&list=PLYxuvEJLss6ByutcqkthikPxV3ccUkwPB

* कोरोना वायरस से जुड़ी सारी प्रामाणिक ख़बरें पढ़ने के लिए क्लिक करें : https://www.bbc.com/hindi/international-51848794

snippet.description:
The #manipur  government has issued "shoot at sight" orders as violence in the state spread to its capital Imphal. Security has been strengthened, with the deployment of 55 army columns. The Rapid Action Force has been flown in. Around 500 personnel of the Rapid Action Force, a riot control police, have been flown in. More than 9,000 people have been rescued from violence-hit areas by the security forces.

snippet.title: Galla’n Ee Ney – Official Video | Satinder Sartaaj, Jatinder Shah | Heli Daruwala
snippet.description:
Here’s VYRL Punjabi and Jatinder Shah presenting #Galla’nEeNey. A heart-wrenching ballad that tells the story of a painful betrayal and the heartbreak that follows. With raw emotion and powerful vocals, Satinder Sartaaj expresses the feeling of being deceived and the anguish of a shattered heart. The haunting melody and poignant lyrics capture the devastation of lost trust. This song is both a tribute to the pain of heartbreak and a reminder of the resilience of the human spirit.

snippet.title: Sakhiye Saheliye (Official) | Godday Godday Chaa | Sonam Bajwa | Tania | Jasmeen | V Rakx Music
snippet.description:
Tips Industries Ltd and Tips Punjabi presents the new Punjabi Song "Sakhiye Saheliye" is from the upcoming movie Godday Godday Chaa. The song is sung by Jasmeen Akhtar, with lyrics penned by Harinder Kour and music composed by Rakesh Raxx. The music video features Sonam Bajwa, Tania, Gitaj Bindrakhia and Gurjazz.

Movie Releasing Worldwide On 26th May 2023.

Sakhiye Saheliya aLso available on:

#sonambajwa #jasmeenakthar #sakhiyesaheliye #gitajbindrakhia #goddaygoddaychaa #tania #newpunjabisong 

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Sakhiye Saheliye Lyrics:

Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sajaa...
Naviye naveliye,
Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khaban vale raah....
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sajaa.
Akhan asmaan vall chuk k tan vekhiye,
Kandhan kaule shattan kolo shutt k tan vekhiye,
Dhup shan de utte haq rakh k tan vekhiye,
Aaja aaja layiye geet zindagi de gaa...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sjaa....
Kandhan kaule, shattan kolon shutt kithe jaavana,
Murh k tan panchi ne aahlane ch aavana,
Ghuggian ne bahuta uchi sikhea na gaavana,
Buk k bathere sanu zindagi de chaa,
Naviye naveliye,
Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khabaa'n vaale raah....
Kholiye jo band pyi khaban di kitab ni,
Haasyean di rutt vala mangiye hisaab ni,
Saukhe ne swaal par aukhe ne jwaab ni,
Nehrea'n nu deyiye jaag chanana'n da laa..
Sakhiye Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,
Mathe utte layiye chan sooraj sjaa....
Suk gye baghan vicho'n labhna ko jhalliye,
Hukama'n ch rahiye bas hukama'n ch chaliye,
Chappa k zameen pairan heth jo swalliye,
Nadiya'n ne muk jana vich dariya...
Naviye naveliye,

Chandan di geliye,
Barhe piche shutt gye ne khabaa'n vaale raah....
Duniya de ranga vich apna v rang hove,
Ajj hoyie kathe fr apna eh kal hove...
Reeta te riwaaz nve ghad lvange,
Dha  k purana raag nva lyie gaa...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Naviye naveliye.
Sakhiye saheliye...
Hath farh mera lyie kafila bna,
Khat k lea de sanu nikke Nike chah,
Gujiye paheliye,
Chandan di galiye...
Fikara nu deyie fook maar k udha,
Sanu v tan thode khamb kholne Sikha...
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye...
Mathe utte lyie chan sooraj sjaa...
Hath farh mera lyie qaafila bna,
Fikara nu deyie fook maar k udha...
Naviye naveliye,
Sakhiye saheliye,
Gujhiye paheliye,

Ek hath reejhan saade ek hath chaa,
Udh jana asi khamb chuni de bna,
Dharti te pair ajj nahio lgda,
Amber v hoyea neeva neeva lgda,
Asin duniya gulaabi rang laini e ranga...

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3763 - 5 May 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3763: Bhide Gets Protective
--------------------------------------------------------
Madhavi seems shy when Bhide makes romantic gestures to her. Later, Sonu approaches her mother for assistance because she is late for college and needs a hand tidying up her tangles. To place an order for pickles and papad, Abdul calls Madhavi. Bhide was acting so romantically that Madhavi thought he was whistling. Because Tapu was calling Sonu in that manner a few hours prior to this incident, Bhide had suspicions about Tapu's version of events. Bhide discovers after checking Sonu's phone that the whistling noise was coming from the ringtone. How would Sonu react when she learns that Bhide is untrustworthy? Stay tuned!

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3763, 5 May 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023

Click here to subscribe to SAB:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Click here to subscribe to SonyLIV: 
http://www.sonyliv.com/signin

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 43 Teaser - 4th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 43 Teaser - 4th May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: Manipur violence: Unease over land and ST status, ground report
snippet.description:
Amid tension over the move to protect forests in the face of resistance from illegal immigrants and also the High Court's direction to include Meitei in scheduled tribes, Internet services have been suspended in the state, informed officials. The Army and Assam Rifles were deployed to control the situation in Manipur where violence broke out during a tribal agitation, a defence spokesperson said on Thursday.

snippet.title: Episode 2 | Yuzvendra Chahal & Kuldeep Yadav | Breakfast with Champions Season 8 | @skodaindia
snippet.description:
A decade ago, Yuzi got Kuldeep caught and bowled on his first class debut. And he’s been getting under Kuldeep’s skin ever since, playing the ‘senior’ card whenever convenient. Perhaps, until now…

What started out as this great rivalry and a competition for the same spot in the Indian white ball team, has developed into an amazing brotherhood where the two of them now are committed to bringing out the best in each other, both on and off the field.

Gaurav Kapur brings the pair together and they chat about a variety of things, including some greats of the game, TV soaps, the correlation between BWC and nuptials, the pranks they’ve pulled, and why it’s time to popularize the hashtag #BechaareBowlers.

This episode of Skoda presents Breakfast with Champions tastes best with a garama-garam KUL-CHA, some chholey, and a side of pyaaz, diced with a sharp CHA-KU.

#GauravKapur #Cricket #SkodaDrivesBWC #BreakfastWithChampions #YuzvendraChahal #KuldeepYadav #IPL #DelhiCapitals #RajasthanRoyals

snippet.title: Thousands participate in 'Tribal Solidarity March' in Manipur
snippet.description:
Thousands of people took part in the 'Tribal Solidarity March' called by a student body in Manipur. They raised slogans opposing the demand for ST status for the Meitei community. The Meiteis inhabit the Manipur valley, which constitutes about 10% of the area of the state.

RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

When a series of women are found dead in public bathrooms under mysterious circumstances, Sub-inspector Anjali Bhaati is tasked with leading the investigation. snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 41 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 3rd May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab

snippet.title: Manipur On The Edge | Army & Assam Rifles Deployed In Manipur To Maintain Peace | Manipur News
snippet.description:
Manipur On The Edge | Army & Assam Rifles Deployed In Manipur To Maintain Peace | Manipur News 


The Army has been summoned to control major violence that ripped through Manipur’s capital Imphal, where multiple vehicles and several places of worship were torched. The most affected areas are Churachandpur and Imphal.


In a desperate plea for assistance, Mary Kom Tweeted: “My state Manipur is burning, kindly help", requesting immediate action from PM Narendra Modi, Home Minister Amit Shah in the matter.


#manipur #indianarmy #violence #shorts #news18 #viral

snippet.title: NEW! Ep 3763 - Tapu Brings Sonu a Sweet Gift?! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | तारक मेहता
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada
Disha Vakani as Daya Jethalal Gada

The Indian Army undertook major rescue operations to evacuate more than 7,500 civilians from all communities throughout the night. The army is also working to restore law and order in Manipur.

snippet.title: गुंडों ने कर लिया Karishma Singh और Pushpa Ji को कैद || Maddam Sir - Ep.29
snippet.description:
गुंडों ने कर लिया Karishma Singh और Pushpa Ji को कैद || Maddam Sir - Ep.29

Show Name – Maddam Sir
Star Cast – Gulki Joshi, Shilpa Shinde, Yukti Kapoor, Sonali Naik, Bhavika Sharma, Pankhuri Awasthy Rode, Priyanshu Singh, and Ajay Jadhav
Produced By – Jay Mehta

#MaddamSir #मैड्डमसर #comedy 

About The Show:
-----------------------------
Set in Lucknow the show is based in one such all-women Police station made by 4 beautiful quirky women. Pushpa, the oldest of them, is the head constable who tries to balance her life between home and work. Karishma, the Sub Inspector, is fish out of the water as she is at loggerheads with the philosophy of the police station. She beats before she talks but now she has to solve all cases through reconciliation. Santosh Sharma is a young new recruit and a typical lonely girl in the city. The head of the pack is S.H.O Haseena Mallik, witty, romantic leads by example. The common challenge for all these women is to bring sensitivity to their policing while dealing with cases that come to this police station. Hence their solution is most unusual. The characters and the cases add to the fun and humor of the show. While Pushpa and Karishma are the saas-bahu duo, who keep us entertained by their Squabbles, it is Haseena - Karishma's ideological differences that add to the drama madam and comedy

snippet.title: Dune: Part Two | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Long Live the Fighters. #DunePartTwo only in theaters November 3.

-----------------
https://www.instagram.com/dunemovie/
https://www.facebook.com/dune
https://twitter.com/dunemovie 
https://www.tiktok.com/@dunemovie 
-----------------
The saga continues as award-winning filmmaker Denis Villeneuve embarks on “Dune: Part Two,” the next chapter of Frank Herbert’s celebrated novel Dune, with an expanded all-star international ensemble cast.  The film, from Warner Bros. Pictures and Legendary Pictures, is the highly anticipated follow-up to 2021’s six-time Academy Award-winning “Dune.”
The big-screen epic continues the adaptation of Frank Herbert’s acclaimed bestseller Dune with returning and new stars, including Oscar nominee Timothée Chalamet (“Wonka,” “Call Me by Your Name”), Zendaya (“Spider-Man: No Way Home,” “Malcolm & Marie,” “Euphoria”), Rebecca Ferguson (“Mission: Impossible – Dead Reckoning”), Oscar nominee Josh Brolin (“Avengers: End Game,” “Milk”), Oscar nominee Austin Butler (“Elvis,” “Once Upon A Time…In Hollywood”), Oscar nominee Florence Pugh (“Black Widow,” “Little Women”), Dave Bautista (the “Guardians of the Galaxy” films, “Thor: Love and Thunder”), Oscar winner Christopher Walken (“The Deer Hunter,” “Hairspray”), Stephen McKinley Henderson (“Fences,” “Lady Bird”), Léa Seydoux (the “James Bond” franchise and “Crimes of the Future”), with Stellan Skarsgård (the “Mamma Mia!” films, “Avengers: Age of Ultron”), with Oscar nominee Charlotte Rampling (“45 Years,” “Assassin’s Creed”), and Oscar winner Javier Bardem (“No Country for Old Men,” “Being the Ricardos”).
“Dune: Part Two” will explore the mythic journey of Paul Atreides as he unites with Chani and the Fremen while on a warpath of revenge against the conspirators who destroyed his family. Facing a choice between the love of his life and the fate of the known universe, he endeavors to prevent a terrible future only he can foresee. 
Villeneuve directed from a screenplay he co-wrote with Jon Spaihts based on Herbert’s novel.  The film is produced by Mary Parent, Cale Boyter, Villeneuve, Tanya Lapointe and Patrick McCormick.  The executive producers are Josh Grode, Herbert W. Gains, Jon Spaihts, Thomas Tull, Brian Herbert, Byron Merritt, Kim Herbert, with Kevin J. Anderson serving as creative consultant.
Villeneuve is again collaborating with his “Dune” creatives: Oscar-winning director of photography Greig Fraser; Oscar-winning production designer Patrice Vermette; Oscar-winning editor Joe Walker; Oscar-winning visual effects supervisor Paul Lambert; Oscar-nominated costume designer Jacqueline West.  Oscar-winning composer Hans Zimmer is again on hand to create the score.
“Dune: Part Two” was filmed on location in Budapest, Abu Dhabi, Jordan and Italy.  The film is slated for a November 3, 2023 worldwide release from Warner Bros. Pictures.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: हरी मिर्च का अचार झटपट बनायें । Instant No cook Green Chilli pickle in 5 minutes  for beginners
snippet.description:
मिर्च मसाला अचार फटाफट बनायें,  No-cook instant chilli pickle recipe - perfect for beginners, hari mirch ka achar banana bataye, hari mirch ka achar kaise dalen, hari mirch ka achar kaise banaya jata hai, 

#chillipickle #instantpickle #mirchkaachar #picklerecipe 

Ingredients for Instant Green Chilli Pickle
हरी मिर्च - Green chilli - 250 grams
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
हल्दी पाउडर - Turmeric powder - 1 tsp
सौंफ पाउडर - Fennel powder - 1 tbsp
राई - Mustard seeds - 2 tbsp, crushed
कश्मीरी लाल मिर्च - Kashmiri red chilli - 1.5 tsp
हींग - Asafoetida - 2 pinch
नमक - Salt - 1 tsp
सरसों का तेल - Mustard oil - 1/4 cup
सिरका - Vinegar - 2 tbsp

snippet.title: Weekly Reliv -Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Episodes 3753-3758 | 24th April To 29th April 2023
snippet.description:
Weekly Reliv is a special compilation of the week’s episodes and is created to give the viewer a feel of the show’s story and its high points. The weekly Reliv here is created especially for the viewers who have missed the week’s episodes and would like to catch up on the plot of their favorite shows. Watch the Weekly Reliv of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah of the episodes from 24th April To 29th April 2023.

Show Name: Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast: Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Raj Anadkat, Amit Bhatt
Episode No: 3753-3758 |  24th April To 29th April 2023
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah 
#तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
#SAB  

Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy:
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - Promoolves around 'Jethalaal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalaal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalaal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son pushes Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalaal.

Click to watch all the Weekly Reliv episodes: https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cQAArE7eMbgq1G5iSXJ7tZC

snippet.title: Balvinder ने Aryan पर तान दी बंदूक | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 704
snippet.description:
Balvinder ने Aryan पर तान दी बंदूक | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 704

After learning the truth about Aryan, Vasundhara reveals his true identity to the Pandey family and wants him to be put behind bars. But Balvinder takes the matter into his own hands and points a gun at Aryan. Will the Pandey family forgive Aryan?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?
